---
title: Mexican Pork & Refried Black Bean Tacos with Charred Capsicum & Chipotle Mayo
description: Tender pork is always a welcomed sight at the dinner table but we’re going a step further and bringing out the welcome committee by adding them to saucy refried bean tacos! Everyone will leave feeling warm and happy, especially when they discover chipotle mayo has joined the party.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65290703b776085eb7bd8b06-2e1822ea.jpeg
